  "title": "SECURITY OFFICER (CONDOMINIUM)",
  "description": "<h3>📅 Work Schedule</h3><ul><li><strong>Day Shift:</strong> 8:00 AM – 8:00 PM</li></ul><h3>👮‍♂️ Rank Available</h3><ul><li><strong>(2) Security Officer</strong></li></ul><h3>📝 Job Responsibilities</h3><ul><li>Conduct access control and ensure only authorized personnel enter the premises.</li><li>Perform foot patrols to maintain safety and security within the residence.</li><li>Monitor CCTV systems and respond to alarms or incidents promptly.</li><li>Assist residents, visitors, and contractors in a courteous manner.</li><li>Report incidents and irregularities according to standard operating procedures.</li></ul><h3>✅ Job Requirements</h3><ul><li>Possess a valid <strong>PLRD Security Licence</strong>.</li><li>Physically fit and alert for long hours of duty.</li><li>Able to communicate basic English clearly.</li><li>Responsible, disciplined, and customer-service oriented.</li><li>Prior residential security experience is an advantage.</li></ul><h3>⭐ What We Offer</h3><ul><li>Stable assignment at a residential site.</li><li>Fixed day shift schedule.</li><li>Supportive team and management.</li><li>Long-term employment opportunities.</li></ul><p>📞 <strong>Interested applicants, whatsapp HR +65 9643 2402 for more information or to apply.</strong></p>",
